title: BATTLE FOR LAND AND SEA - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Mod Gameplay
description:
BATTLE FOR LAND AND SEA - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Mod Gameplay - The Empire of Nicaea is in a bloody civil war and look to allies outside of their kingdom. This is a 2v2 Online Battle.  Fought both on land and sea!  Enjoy the Battle :D

Lighting Mod: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=532125259&searchtext=aztec

Realistic Ground - http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=869415580&searchtext=
